<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="et">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Kontakt - Paul Keres</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lilita+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    </head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-container">
            <h1>  Kontakt </h1>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Avaleht</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">Info</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/estonian-news">Eesti Uudised</a></li>

                </ul>
            </nav>
            <a href="/profile"class="profile-link"> <%= user.username %></a>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Kontakt</h1>
        <div class="text-content">
            <p>Kui soovite rohkem teavet või soovite meiega ühendust võtta, siis palun kasutage allpool olevaid kontakte:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>E-post: paul.keres@mail.ee</li>
                <li>Telefon: +372 5686 2001</li>
                <li>Aadress: Maleva 5, 10117 Tallinn, Eesti</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <h1>Tagasiside</h1>
        <ul>
            <% feedback.forEach((fb) => { %>
                <li> <%= fb.message %></li>
            <% }); %>
        </ul>        
        
        <form action="/submit-feedback" method="post">
            <textarea name="message" placeholder="Teie tagasiside" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Saada tagasiside</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body> 
</html>
